  "title": "Retail Sales Associates (Islandwide)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Demonstrate and provide product information and answer all enquires</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent customer service and ensure customers are satisfied with the overall purchase experience</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain good relationship with customers</li>\n  <li>Provide product demonstrations and educate customers on the proper usage, care, and maintenance of products</li>\n  <li>Engage with customers, understanding their needs and provide advice and guidance on products selection</li>\n  <li>Maintain a clean and organized sales floor, regularly restocking inventory and organizing product displays to enhance the shopping experience.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the sales team and store management to achieve daily and monthly sales targets.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
